# CouncilSidebar

A sidebar component displaying council/government members with automatic position-based sorting.

## Import

```typescript
import { CouncilSidebar } from '@happyvertical/svelte';
```

## Basic Usage

<div class="example">
  <div class="example-preview" style="width: 100%; max-width: 300px;">
    <CouncilSidebar councilName="Town of Bentley Council" members={sampleMembers} />
  </div>
</div>

```svelte
<script>
  const members = [
    { name: 'John Smith', position: 'Mayor' },
    { name: 'Jane Doe', position: 'Deputy Mayor' },
    { name: 'Bob Wilson', position: 'Councillor', ward: 'Ward 1' },
    { name: 'Alice Brown', position: 'Councillor', ward: 'Ward 2' }
  ];
</script>

<CouncilSidebar councilName="Town Council" {members} />
```

